{"tid":1578784,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港近期多人離世 是否真的與831太子案有關？〈蕭若元：理論蕭析","createTime":"2019-09-18T09:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T17:57:29.000Z","uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1504c4cdf8b6775bc92449ac3d1bc073d8217988","tid":1578784,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/I8HIai1w0Ko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI8HIai1w0Ko&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj8yZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=1bea25bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/I8HIai1w0Ko</a>"},{"pid":"20252df3939fb1f8a3c26037160f1e833f8bcace","tid":1578784,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, 當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b4f0d34ad675909eac8f2bf76860682c63184b38","tid":1578784,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y27s29y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY27s29y.png&h=9ca19531&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ff64b9983805eb25e35d64f1c8d5874dc0905de","tid":1578784,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.ytimg.com/vi/cAlsxbRkQVc/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FcAlsxbRkQVc%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=8fda9325&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"caf2bf474db0b57c058ec73963d1b99c82e06fa3","tid":1578784,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:26:34.000Z","msg":"蕭生話有個自稱做學術研究的雲吞博士網友做左個自殺分析<br />\n由6月12起，平均每十日香港就有十人自殺<br />\n由821到831，數字上升到十八個<br />\n由9月1到9月10，個案升到二十八個，即係一日有2.8人自殺"},{"pid":"93272031ee4d079a4c392a7a1d2634193a17e2b8","tid":1578784,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:34:38.000Z","msg":"蕭生話根據防止自殺會的數據，每十日有二十五人自殺先岩，果個網友只係從新聞收集數據，而有啲自殺個案新聞根本無報到"},{"pid":"3696c83a717b6fc584dbfa6b24342354b239029b","tid":1578784,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T17:57:29.000Z","msg":"蕭生話有個網友同佢講左件事令佢好surprise：該網友個仔今年讀小六，班上有個同學嘅屋企人係做警察。開左學咁耐班上係無人同嗰個同學講過一句嘢。"}]}